high_descs: turn right, go to left end of green dresser with red clock
pick up cell phone on left corner of green dresser
turn around, go to right side of bed with purple pillow
place phone on bed to the right of purple pillow
turn around, go to green dresser to the right
pick up cell phone in between credit card and cell phone
turn around, go to right side of bed with purple pillow and cell phone
place cell phone to the right of cell phone
anns.task_desc: place two cell phones on bed to the right of purple pillow

high_descs: Walk up to the bed, then turn right and walk over to the dresser.
Pick up the leftmost phone off of the dresser.
Turn right and take a step forward, then walk over to the side of the bed.
Put the phone on the edge of the bed to the right of the purple pillow.
Walk back over to the dresser.
Pick up the leftmost phone off of the dresser.
Turn left and walk back over to the side of the bed.
Put the phone on the bed to the right of the phone that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two phones to a bed.

high_descs: Turn right and face the box in front of you.
Take the phone off the table in front of you.
Turn left then face the bed to your left.
Place the phone on the bed in front of you.
Turn left and face the table to your left.
Take the phone from the table in front of you.
Turn left and face the bed to your left.
Place the phone on the bed in front of you.
